content: {"name": "360 EATS INC-The Mattie Williams Neighborhood Family Center", "alternate_name": "", "description": "Free Mobile Meal Program (Food Truck) - serves free, chef-prepared, nutritious, gourmet meals to anyone in need of food assistance via our Sustain-A-Bowl food truck.
